Computes w from modified Corrado-Su model.

Source: R/csm.R
csmw.Rd

w formula implementation from modified Corrado-Su model.

Usage

csmw(sigma, time, mu3, mu4)

Arguments

sigma

volatility of the stock price.

time

time to option expiration in years.

mu3

skewness.

mu4

kurtosis.

Value

Vector with w.

Recycle rule

These arguments handle the recycle rule so vectors can be provided and once those vectors differs in length the recycle rule is applied.

See also

csmd for d from modified Corrado-Su model.\ csmq3 for Q_3 from modified Corrado-Su model.\ csmq4 for Q_4 from modified Corrado-Su model.\ csmprice for modified Corrado-Su option pricing formula.

Examples
